response.original_title: Ken Davis Live: Under the Influence
response.overview: Ken Davis is "Under the Influence" but it is not what you think.  Recorded live in two sold-out shows in the middle of a thunderstorm, this is Ken's best performance yet! Ken's hilarious stories include, "Strawberry Underwear", the "Kansas Cow", "Hurricane Man", "The Speeding Ticket", "Teenage Mutant Hotel Dwellers" and a whole lot more! You'll laugh till your sides ache, and you'll be encouraged to live "under the influence". This is a bold declaration of Ken's faith. As always, the whole family will love this DVD.
response.title: Ken Davis Live: Under the Influence
